Main use cases: 13/10
- Create reservation
- Check-in and check out
- Take orders
- Pay now/later


Classes:
	MenuItem
- Name: String
- Ingredients: [String]*
- instruction: String
- Cost: Double


	Order 
- OrderNo: Int
- TableNo: Int
- TotalCost: Double
- FoodOrder: [MenuItem]
- Allergens/Extra Info: String
- IsPaid: boolean
- ————————
- Void PayNow(int orderID)
- Void PayLater(int orderID)
- Void ViewOrder()

Reservation
- ID: int
- Name: String
- ReservationDate: DateTime
- Address: String
- Phone: Int
- ClientDetail: String
- RoomType: String
- Packages: [String] (breakfast, leisure centre)
- Cost: Double
- —————
- Void Checkin(int reservationID)
- Void Checkin(int reservationID)


